---
title: Chargrilled Pumpkin & Chorizo Couscous with Lemon Yoghurt & Parsley
description: Here’s another epic BBQ feast to spice up your mealtime. Packed with smokey chorizo, pumpkin, and a zesty dollop of lemon yoghurt, this heartwarming bowl of fluffy couscous is piled high with colours and flavours. Tear over some fresh parsley and dig in! No BBQ? Follow along with our stovetop method.
